ouichi-kimuras-cozy-house-is-a-secluded-space-in-a-busy-japan-neighborhood/" class="main_carousel_link"><img src="http://assets.inhabitat.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2015/04/Cozy-House-FORM-1-150x100.jpg" width="149" height="100" style="margin-top:0!important;" alt="" /></a></div><div id="carousel-summary_733399" class="carousel-summary carousel-summary-" style="width:149px;display:none;height: 40px; top: -40px;"><div class="hidden-title"><h4><a href="http://inhabitat.com/kouichi-kimuras-cozy-house-is-a-secluded-space-in-a-busy-japan-neighborhood/" >Kouichi Kimura's Cozy House is a&hellip;</a></h4></div></div></div></div></div><script type='text/javascript' src='http://assets.inhabitat.com/wp-content/themes/inhabitat-v3/js/stepcarousel_include-sidebar-2.js'></script></div><a class="widget-carousel-prev" href="javascript:stepcarousel.stepBy('mygallery', -1)" id="advcarousel-prev">Prev</a>
