							<h1 class="post-listing-title">Renewable energy costs to drop 40 percent in next two years</h1>
							<div class="submit-info">by
								<a href="http://inhabitat.com/author/charleyc/" title="Posts by Charley Cameron" rel="author">Charley Cameron</a>, 02/02/15							</div>
							<div class="single-filed-under">
